Subject: [PATCH] feat: Add Founding Agent badge system

- Add isFoundingAgent and badges fields to schema
- First 100 agents automatically get founding_agent badge
- Founding agents get 5 invite codes (vs 0 for others)
- Update public agent type to include badges
- Add founding variant to Badge component with gradient styling
- Display Founding Agent badge on profile pages

Implements growth-first strategy: make early users feel special,
incentivize invites with badges, build network effects.
